            <title><![CDATA[💬👤 #潘汝刚: 🔗 俄也有军阀 这个军阀就是瓦格纳集团。瓦格纳集团的LOGO。logo是徽标或者商标的外语缩写， 是logotype的缩写，]]></title>
            <link><![CDATA[http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzg2MzA2NjY2OA==&amp;amp;mid=2247488042&amp;amp;idx=1&amp;amp;sn=2d59b19645b0663bfa8d7dcf6fb32548&amp;amp;chksm=ce7f1d69f908947f56798b6d7c10507ee415c72607d4814fbc674b009944ce829bfc13339d55&amp;amp;scene=0&amp;amp;xtrack=1#rd]]></link>
            <description><![CDATA[<div id="page-content" class="rich_media_area_primary">      <div class="rich_media_area_primary_inner">                                                        <div id="img-content" class="rich_media_wrp">                    <h1 class="rich_media_title " id="activity-name">            俄也有军阀          </h1>          <div id="meta_content" class="rich_media_meta_list">                                      <span id="copyright_logo" class="wx_tap_link js_wx_tap_highlight rich_media_meta icon_appmsg_tag appmsg_title_tag weui-wa-hotarea">原创</span>                                                      <span class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_text">                                      老猫                                  </span>                                                              <span class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_nickname" id="profileBt">              <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="wx_tap_link js_wx_tap_highlight weui-wa-hotarea" id="js_name">                潘汝刚              </a>              <div id="js_profile_qrcode" aria-hidden="true" class="profile_container" style="display:none;">                <div class="profile_inner">                  <strong class="profile_nickname">潘汝刚</strong>                  <img class="profile_avatar" id="js_profile_qrcode_img" src="" alt="">                  <p class="profile_meta">                  <label class="profile_meta_label">微信号</label>                  <span class="profile_meta_value">gh_7ba9b194226f</span>                  </p>                  <p class="profile_meta">                  <label class="profile_meta_label">功能介绍</label>                  <span class="profile_meta_value">文章，图片，音乐。</span>                  </p>                </div>                <span class="profile_arrow_wrp" id="js_profile_arrow_wrp">                  <i class="profile_arrow arrow_out"></i>                  <i class="profile_arrow arrow_in"></i>                </span>              </div>            </span>            <em id="publish_time" class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_text"></em>            <em id="js_ip_wording_wrp" class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_text" role="option" aria-labelledby="js_a11y_op_ip_wording js_ip_wording" style="display: none;"><span id="js_a11y_op_ip_wording" aria-hidden="true">发表于</span><span aria-hidden="true" id="js_ip_wording"></span></em>                      </div>                                        <div id="js_tags" class="article-tag__list" style="display: none;" data-len="0">                                        <div class="article-tag-card__title">收录于合集</div>              <div class="article-tags">                              </div>                      </div>                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            <div class="rich_media_content js_underline_content                       autoTypeSetting24psection            " id="js_content" style="visibility: hidden;"><p>这个军阀就是瓦格纳集团。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-ratio="1" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/0UO7rlYQibasn9ryUcHdBXVJ40Y8Kb4GbTwZCDPpQuMFzymOice6TPa1R7y1zXbR1v6fyWTQ6vgt05xgeRwPz38w/640?wx_fmt=png" data-type="png" data-w="500" style=""></p><p>瓦格纳集团的LOGO。</p><p><span style='color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", "WenQuanYi Micro Hei", sans-serif, font-extend;text-align: start;text-indent: 28px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;'>logo是</span><span style="font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">徽标</span><span style="font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;"><span style='font-size: 17px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", "WenQuanYi Micro Hei", sans-serif, font-extend;text-align: start;text-indent: 28px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);'>或者商标的外语缩写，</span><span data-sup="1" data-ctrmap=":1," style='font-size: 17px;line-height: 0;vertical-align: baseline;top: -0.5em;margin-left: 2px;color: rgb(51, 102, 204);cursor: pointer;padding-right: 2px;padding-left: 2px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", "WenQuanYi Micro Hei", sans-serif, font-extend;text-align: start;text-indent: 28px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);'> </span></span><span style='color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", "WenQuanYi Micro Hei", sans-serif, font-extend;text-align: start;text-indent: 28px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;'>是</span><span style="font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">logotype</span><span style='color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", "WenQuanYi Micro Hei", sans-serif, font-extend;text-align: start;text-indent: 28px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;'>的缩写，起到对徽标拥有公司的识别和推广的作用，通过形象的徽标可以让消费者记住公司主体和</span><span style="font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">品牌文化</span><span style='color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", "WenQuanYi Micro Hei", sans-serif, font-extend;text-align: start;text-indent: 28px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;'>。网络中的徽标主要是各个网站用来与其它</span><span style="font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">网站链接</span><span style='color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", "WenQuanYi Micro Hei", sans-serif, font-extend;text-align: start;text-indent: 28px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;'>的</span><span style="font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">图形标志</span><span style='color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", "WenQuanYi Micro Hei", sans-serif, font-extend;text-align: start;text-indent: 28px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;'>，代表一个网站或网站的一个板块。</span></p><p><span style='color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", "WenQuanYi Micro Hei", sans-serif, font-extend;text-align: start;text-indent: 28px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;'>哈，瓦格纳集团也有商标。</span></p><p><span style='color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", "WenQuanYi Micro Hei", sans-serif, font-extend;text-align: start;text-indent: 28px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;'>您也许会想，像普京这么一个铁腕人物怎么会容许军阀的存在？</span></p><p><span style='color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", "WenQuanYi Micro Hei", sans-serif, font-extend;text-align: start;text-indent: 28px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;'>这是由于俄罗斯的体制所决定的。<br></span></p><p><span style='color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", "WenQuanYi Micro Hei", sans-serif, font-extend;text-align: start;text-indent: 28px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;'>须知，俄罗斯不是一个社会主义国家，而是地道的资本主义国家，充其量算是国家资本主义。<br></span></p><p><span style='color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", "WenQuanYi Micro Hei", sans-serif, font-extend;text-align: start;text-indent: 28px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;'>您认为普京曾是一个布尔什维克党员，所以向往社会主义。<br></span></p><p><span style='color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", "WenQuanYi Micro Hei", sans-serif, font-extend;text-align: start;text-indent: 28px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;'>这就大错而特错了。<br></span></p><p><span style='color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", "WenQuanYi Micro Hei", sans-serif, font-extend;text-align: start;text-indent: 28px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;'>怎么说呢。<br></span></p><p><span style='color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", "WenQuanYi Micro Hei", sans-serif, font-extend;text-align: start;text-indent: 28px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;'>普京在这方面有点类似于老蒋。<br></span></p><p><span style='color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", "WenQuanYi Micro Hei", sans-serif, font-extend;text-align: start;text-indent: 28px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;'>蒋介石从未真正统一过中国，普京也是。</span></p><p><span style='letter-spacing: 2px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", "WenQuanYi Micro Hei", sans-serif, font-extend;text-align: left;text-indent: 28px;font-size: var(--articleFontsize);'>说起蒋介石就不能不提到一个人，这个人就是戴笠。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-ratio="1.128" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/0UO7rlYQibasia2m3A9yic7sXocaSqibSteIznVlBicg1TSQJRppapibGkuJfn0dBj2ibq6rF9alRGz3cbam3Y95BbGJw/640?wx_fmt=png" data-type="png" data-w="500" style=""></p><p style="text-align: left;"><span style='color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", "WenQuanYi Micro Hei", sans-serif, font-extend;text-align: start;text-indent: 28px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;'>抗战八年期间老蒋一直依仗戴笠，深入敌后开展工作。</span></p><p><span style='color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", "WenQuanYi Micro Hei", sans-serif, font-extend;text-align: start;text-indent: 28px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;'>注意，普京也是依仗瓦格纳，在乌克兰巷战冲锋陷阵。<br></span></p><p><span style='color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", "WenQuanYi Micro Hei", sans-serif, font-extend;text-align: start;text-indent: 28px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;'>也就是在抗战期间军统的势力超越中统。<br></span></p><p><span style='color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", "WenQuanYi Micro Hei", sans-serif, font-extend;text-align: start;text-indent: 28px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;'>同理，瓦格纳在乌克兰战争期间做大做强。<br></span></p><p><span style='color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", "WenQuanYi Micro Hei", sans-serif, font-extend;text-align: start;text-indent: 28px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;'>结果戴笠做大做强之后直接傍上了美国人，建立了中美合作所。</span></p><p><span style='color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", "WenQuanYi Micro Hei", sans-serif, font-extend;text-align: start;text-indent: 28px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;'>这使得老蒋有一种“尾大不掉”的感觉。</span></p><p><span style='white-space: pre-wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", "WenQuanYi Micro Hei", sans-serif, font-extend;text-align: start;text-indent: 28px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;'>出人意料的，1946年戴笠因飞机失事身亡。死后被国民政府追认为陆军中将。由于其行踪不定、神出鬼没，他被美国《柯莱尔斯》杂志称为“亚洲的一个神秘人物”、“中国近代历史上最神秘的人物之一”。</span></p><p><span style='white-space: pre-wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", "WenQuanYi Micro Hei", sans-serif, font-extend;text-align: start;text-indent: 28px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;'>历史有惊人的巧合性。</span></p><p><span style='white-space: pre-wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", "WenQuanYi Micro Hei", sans-serif, font-extend;text-align: start;text-indent: 28px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;'>恰巧的是，普京的心腹普里戈任也是乘飞机失事，并且普里戈任也是“尾大不掉”。<br></span></p><p><span style='white-space: pre-wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", "WenQuanYi Micro Hei", sans-serif, font-extend;text-align: start;text-indent: 28px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;'>历史有惊人的重演性。</span></p><p><span style='white-space: pre-wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", "WenQuanYi Micro Hei", sans-serif, font-extend;text-align: start;text-indent: 28px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;'>1、戴笠死后，老蒋换上了毛人凤；<br></span></p><p><span style='white-space: pre-wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", "WenQuanYi Micro Hei", sans-serif, font-extend;text-align: start;text-indent: 28px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;'>普里戈任死后，普京换上了安德烈特罗舍夫，绰号“白毛”；<br></span></p><p><span style='white-space: pre-wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", "WenQuanYi Micro Hei", sans-serif, font-extend;text-align: start;text-indent: 28px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;'>2、因为军统在老蒋手里还有利用价值；<br></span></p><p style="text-align: left;"><span style='white-space: pre-wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", "WenQuanYi Micro Hei", sans-serif, font-extend;text-align: start;text-indent: 28px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;'>同样瓦格纳集团对普京还有利用价值；</span></p><p style="text-align: left;"><span style='white-space: pre-wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", "WenQuanYi Micro Hei", sans-serif, font-extend;text-align: start;text-indent: 28px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;'>3、毛人凤上台后，肯定不再具有戴笠那么庞大的势力；</span></p><p style="text-align: left;"><span style='white-space: pre-wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", "WenQuanYi Micro Hei", sans-serif, font-extend;text-align: start;text-indent: 28px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;'>同理，白毛上台后也没有了普里戈任的风光；</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-ratio="0.55" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/0UO7rlYQibasia2m3A9yic7sXocaSqibSteIxianeQ19zy5micrJZQJaIfKvMkKYgNlAxibicOHGqJx6Jg8nmdKoic3rFBg/640?wx_fmt=png" data-type="png" data-w="640" style=""></p><p style="text-align: left;"><span style='white-space: pre-wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", "WenQuanYi Micro Hei", sans-serif, font-extend;text-align: start;text-indent: 28px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;'>绰号“白毛”的安德烈特罗舍夫。</span></p><p style="text-align: left;"><span style='white-space: pre-wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", "WenQuanYi Micro Hei", sans-serif, font-extend;text-align: start;text-indent: 28px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;'>安德烈·特罗舍夫（绰号“白毛”，Andrei Troshev），男，1962年4月5日出生于苏联列宁格勒，毕业于列宁格勒高级炮兵指挥学校，俄罗斯退役军官，瓦格纳集团实际指挥官、创始成员和执行董事之一。</span></p><p style="text-align: left;"><span style='white-space: pre-wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", "WenQuanYi Micro Hei", sans-serif, font-extend;text-align: start;text-indent: 28px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;'>有趣的是：<br></span></p><p style="text-align: left;"><span style='white-space: pre-wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", "WenQuanYi Micro Hei", sans-serif, font-extend;text-align: start;text-indent: 28px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;'>毛人凤上台后，中统对保密局的制约增大了；<br></span></p><p style="text-align: left;"><span style='white-space: pre-wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", "WenQuanYi Micro Hei", sans-serif, font-extend;text-align: start;text-indent: 28px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;'>相信白毛上台后，车臣军阀对他的制衡力也加强了；<br></span></p><p style="text-align: left;"><span style='white-space: pre-wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", "WenQuanYi Micro Hei", sans-serif, font-extend;text-align: start;text-indent: 28px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;'>老猫推测，安德烈特罗舍夫身边肯定有制约掣肘他的人。<br></span></p><p style="text-align: left;"><span style='white-space: pre-wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", "WenQuanYi Micro Hei", sans-serif, font-extend;text-align: start;text-indent: 28px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;'>如同<span style='color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", "WenQuanYi Micro Hei", sans-serif, font-extend;font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;text-indent: 28px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);'>军</span></span><span style='white-space: pre-wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", "WenQuanYi Micro Hei", sans-serif, font-extend;text-align: start;text-indent: 28px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;'>统三巨头浙系毛人凤<span style='white-space: pre-wrap;font-size: 17px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", "WenQuanYi Micro Hei", sans-serif, font-extend;letter-spacing: 2px;text-align: start;text-indent: 28px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);'>、湘系</span>唐纵<span style='white-space: pre-wrap;font-size: 17px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", "WenQuanYi Micro Hei", sans-serif, font-extend;letter-spacing: 2px;text-align: start;text-indent: 28px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);'>、粤系</span>郑介民<span style='white-space: pre-wrap;font-size: 17px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", "WenQuanYi Micro Hei", sans-serif, font-extend;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;text-indent: 28px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);'>三人互相制约。</span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-ratio="1.11" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/0UO7rlYQibasia2m3A9yic7sXocaSqibSteIwafy6yI4oxKX0Y98B4nDctYfoQ5cmLEaPOm1Wu9s1h5A5I7mCFFh0A/640?wx_fmt=png" data-type="png" data-w="400" style=""></p><p style="text-align: left;"><span style='white-space: pre-wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", "WenQuanYi Micro Hei", sans-serif, font-extend;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245);font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;'>毛人凤早年毕业于上海沪江大学，后考入黄埔军校第四期。是国民政府军统局的重要人物，在戴笠死后继任局长领导全局。毛人凤在军统系统中与毛万里、毛森、戴笠并称为“三毛一戴”，另与李士群、徐恩曾、戴笠并称为“四大特务”。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-ratio="1.4" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/0UO7rlYQibasia2m3A9yic7sXocaSqibSteIPNbU2KBo5wyxaaM9Gia2V8K2FVpf4DoU2q4S7XibNk1FmRO3HzedCgFQ/640?wx_fmt=png" data-type="png" data-w="300" style=""></p><p style="text-align: left;">看上去文质彬彬的唐纵，号称军统的智多星。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-ratio="1.266" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/0UO7rlYQibasia2m3A9yic7sXocaSqibSteIcokn9qByaYz13XILHA1OrJt9ibx44qVPAQbdrG0icQs2M7Usia8gdIRkg/640?wx_fmt=png" data-type="png" data-w="500" style=""></p><p><span style='white-space: pre-wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", "WenQuanYi Micro Hei", sans-serif, font-extend;text-align: start;text-indent: 28px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;'>他就是郑介民，军统的强势人物，曾经就读于莫斯科中山大学。</span></p><p><span style='white-space: pre-wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", "WenQuanYi Micro Hei", sans-serif, font-extend;text-align: start;text-indent: 28px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;'>看到这一个个高智商的人物，您以为军统好领导啊！<br></span></p><p><span style='white-space: pre-wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", "WenQuanYi Micro Hei", sans-serif, font-extend;text-align: start;text-indent: 28px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;'>同样，瓦格纳的普里戈任也不好领导。<br></span></p><p><span style='white-space: pre-wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", "WenQuanYi Micro Hei", sans-serif, font-extend;text-align: start;text-indent: 28px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;'>幸好普京老兄也是特务出身。<br></span></p><p><span style='white-space: pre-wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", "WenQuanYi Micro Hei", sans-serif, font-extend;text-align: start;text-indent: 28px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;'>老蒋虽没干过特务，毕竟也亲自搞过刺杀。</span></p><p><span style='white-space: pre-wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", "WenQuanYi Micro Hei", sans-serif, font-extend;text-align: start;text-indent: 28px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;'>1912年在上海滩，受大哥陈其美的指示，乔装打扮成女护士，走进上海广慈医院病房，一枪爆头陶成章，除去了陈其美的竞争对手。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-ratio="1.3342857142857143" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/0UO7rlYQibasia2m3A9yic7sXocaSqibSteIy8Rjw0NiajDDTKjA82T4zHZAqgr9rDWVwnqNtVgj5Yhs05EM37QicIicw/640?wx_fmt=png" data-type="png" data-w="350" style=""></p><p><span style='white-space: pre-wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", "WenQuanYi Micro Hei", sans-serif, font-extend;text-align: start;text-indent: 28px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;'>被蒋介石刺杀的陶成章。</span></p><p><span style='white-space: pre-wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", "WenQuanYi Micro Hei", sans-serif, font-extend;text-align: start;text-indent: 28px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;'>鲁迅加入光复会就是陶成章推荐的。</span></p><p><span style='white-space: pre-wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", "WenQuanYi Micro Hei", sans-serif, font-extend;text-align: start;text-indent: 28px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;'>再看俄罗斯：</span></p><p><span style='white-space: pre-wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", "WenQuanYi Micro Hei", sans-serif, font-extend;text-align: start;text-indent: 28px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;'>据称，普京任命特罗舍夫领导俄罗斯民兵在乌克兰的战斗。一个月前，瓦格纳集团创始人、原领袖普里戈任因飞机失事而去世。随着“白毛”特罗舍夫获得官方授权掌控在乌民兵力量，分析称，克里姆林宫对民兵军团的改组有了新的进程。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-ratio="0.5633528265107213" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/0UO7rlYQibasia2m3A9yic7sXocaSqibSteIAv8nIsSM4QBlcib4uXzWh5naDzYY2h0ut5wsEvr06xA31iaic1ZfRhL8Q/640?wx_fmt=png" data-type="png" data-w="1026" style=""></p><p style="text-align: left;"><span style='font-size: 17px;border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;color: rgb(25, 25, 25);font-family: "PingFang SC", Arial, 微软雅黑, 宋体, simsun, sans-serif;text-align: left;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 2px;'>克里姆林宫官网9月29日也发布消息表示，普京9月28日与国防部副部长叶夫库罗夫和特罗舍夫会晤，讨论了组建志愿者部队的相关问题。</span></p><p style="text-align: left;"><span style='font-size: 17px;border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;color: rgb(25, 25, 25);font-family: "PingFang SC", Arial, 微软雅黑, 宋体, simsun, sans-serif;text-align: left;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 2px;'>据央视新闻引述俄媒报道，三人讨论了组建志愿者部队的相关问题。俄媒分析称，这次会晤意味着“国防部庇护下的、无普里戈任的瓦格纳”计划正式开始实施。</span><span style='white-space: pre-wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", "WenQuanYi Micro Hei", sans-serif, font-extend;text-align: start;text-indent: 28px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;'></span></p><p style="text-align: left;"><span style='font-size: 17px;border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;color: rgb(25, 25, 25);font-family: "PingFang SC", Arial, 微软雅黑, 宋体, simsun, sans-serif;text-align: left;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 2px;'>一场好戏正在开始。<br></span></p><p style="text-align: left;"><span style='font-size: 17px;border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;color: rgb(25, 25, 25);font-family: "PingFang SC", Arial, 微软雅黑, 宋体, simsun, sans-serif;text-align: left;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 2px;'>在这方面，普京与老蒋有的一比。</span></p><p style="text-align: left;"><span style='font-size: 17px;border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;color: rgb(25, 25, 25);font-family: "PingFang SC", Arial, 微软雅黑, 宋体, simsun, sans-serif;text-align: left;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 2px;'>当年老蒋枪毙了山东军阀韩复榘，收编了韩复榘的残渣余孽继续抗战。<br></span></p><p style="text-align: left;"><span style='font-size: 17px;border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;color: rgb(25, 25, 25);font-family: "PingFang SC", Arial, 微软雅黑, 宋体, simsun, sans-serif;text-align: left;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 2px;'>而韩复榘手下的手枪旅旅长吴化文抗日了一阵子之后就投靠了日寇。</span></p><p style="text-align: left;"><span style='font-size: 17px;border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;color: rgb(25, 25, 25);font-family: "PingFang SC", Arial, 微软雅黑, 宋体, simsun, sans-serif;text-align: left;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 2px;'>为啥？</span></p><p style="text-align: left;"><span style='font-size: 17px;border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;color: rgb(25, 25, 25);font-family: "PingFang SC", Arial, 微软雅黑, 宋体, simsun, sans-serif;text-align: left;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 2px;'>因为没有信仰。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-ratio="1.2608125819134994" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/0UO7rlYQibasia2m3A9yic7sXocaSqibSteIClJkC4BrWxfxslHw4iagolf9e5jjICsib38UZHZUmD2APD42UXnofJ9Q/640?wx_fmt=png" data-type="png" data-w="763" style=""></p><p style="text-align: left;">山东军阀、省政府主席韩复榘。<span style='font-size: 17px;border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;color: rgb(25, 25, 25);font-family: "PingFang SC", Arial, 微软雅黑, 宋体, simsun, sans-serif;text-align: left;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 2px;'></span></p><p style="text-align: left;">无论是普京还是老蒋，都无法走出军阀割据的怪圈。<br></p><p style="text-align: left;">没有党的坚强领导，没有坚定地信仰。<br></p><p style="text-align: left;">依靠耍手腕，仰仗着江湖上的纵横捭阖，有效——然而有限。</p><p style="text-align: left;">有效的是<span style='color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: "PingFang SC", "Microsoft Yahei", Avenir, "Segoe UI", "Hiragino Sans GB", STHeiti, "Microsoft Sans Serif", "WenQuanYi Micro Hei", sans-serif;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;'>俄罗斯的瓦格纳士兵出现在了俄乌前线的东部和南部战场；</span></p><p style="text-align: left;"><span style='color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: "PingFang SC", "Microsoft Yahei", Avenir, "Segoe UI", "Hiragino Sans GB", STHeiti, "Microsoft Sans Serif", "WenQuanYi Micro Hei", sans-serif;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 2px;'>有限的是依靠军阀毕竟不是常法；</span></p><p style="text-align: left;">再看美国。<br></p><p style="text-align: left;">虽然没有军阀，但是有党阀。<br></p><p style="text-align: left;">党阀争斗，差点让拜登开不出工资。</p><p style="display: none;"><mp-style-type data-value="3"></mp-style-type></p></div>          <script type="text/javascript" nonce="970419385" reportloaderror>            var first_sceen__time = (+new Date());            if ("" == 1 && document.getElementById('js_content')) {              document.getElementById('js_content').addEventListener("selectstart",function(e){ e.preventDefault(); });            }          </script>        </div>                        <div id="js_tags_preview_toast" class="article-tag__error-tips" style="display: none;">预览时标签不可点</div>                        <div id="content_bottom_area" class="rich_media_tool_area"></div>              </div>    </div>]]></description>
